<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6c8ddb40-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s3904"><num value="3904">§ 3904.</num><heading> Eligible entities</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The following entities are eligible to receive assistance under this chapter:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id6c8ddb41-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s3904/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> A corporation.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id6c8ddb42-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s3904/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> A partnership.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id6c8ddb43-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s3904/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> A joint venture.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id6c8ddb44-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s3904/4"><num value="4">(4)</num><content> A trust.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id6c8ddb45-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s3904/5"><num value="5">(5)</num><content> A Federal, State, or local governmental entity, agency, or instrumentality.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id6c8ddb46-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s3904/6"><num value="6">(6)</num><content> A tribal government or consortium of tribal governments.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id6c8ddb47-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s3904/7"><num value="7">(7)</num><content> A State infrastructure financing authority.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id6c8ddb48-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e">(<ref href="/us/pl/113/121/tV/s5025">Pub. L. 113–121, title V, § 5025</ref>, <date date="2014-06-10">June 10, 2014</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/128/1334">128 Stat. 1334</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
